' =====================================================
' Relationships
' =====================================================

' Inheritance / Extension
ToolContext --|> RunContextWrapper : extends
ToolOutputGuardrailData --|> ToolInputGuardrailData : extends

' Tool Identity
ToolOrigin *-- ToolOriginType : type

' FunctionTool core relationships
FunctionTool *-- "0..*" ToolInputGuardrail : tool_input_guardrails
FunctionTool *-- "0..*" ToolOutputGuardrail : tool_output_guardrails
FunctionTool o-- ToolOrigin : _tool_origin
FunctionTool ..> ToolContext : on_invoke_tool(ctx, args)

' FunctionToolResult
FunctionToolResult *-- FunctionTool : tool

' Function Schema pipeline
FuncDocumentation ..> FuncSchema : consumed by function_schema()
FuncSchema ..> FunctionTool : params_json_schema supplied to

' Tool Guardrail execution flow
ToolInputGuardrail ..> ToolInputGuardrailData : consumes
ToolInputGuardrail ..> ToolInputGuardrailResult : produces
ToolOutputGuardrail ..> ToolOutputGuardrailData : consumes
ToolOutputGuardrail ..> ToolOutputGuardrailResult : produces

ToolInputGuardrailResult *-- ToolInputGuardrail : guardrail
ToolInputGuardrailResult *-- ToolGuardrailFunctionOutput : output
ToolOutputGuardrailResult *-- ToolOutputGuardrail : guardrail
ToolOutputGuardrailResult *-- ToolGuardrailFunctionOutput : output

ToolInputGuardrailData *-- ToolContext : context

' Guardrail behavior variants
ToolGuardrailFunctionOutput ..> AllowBehavior : behavior
ToolGuardrailFunctionOutput ..> RejectContentBehavior : behavior
ToolGuardrailFunctionOutput ..> RaiseExceptionBehavior : behavior

' Agent-level guardrail execution flow
InputGuardrail ..> InputGuardrailResult : produces
OutputGuardrail ..> OutputGuardrailResult : produces
InputGuardrailResult *-- GuardrailFunctionOutput : output
OutputGuardrailResult *-- GuardrailFunctionOutput : output

' Deferred loading connection
ToolSearchTool ..> FunctionTool : loads deferred tools\n(defer_loading=True)

' =====================================================
' Annotations
' =====================================================
note bottom of FunctionTool
  **@function_tool** decorator wraps a Python function as FunctionTool.
  **defer_loading=True** hides tool until ToolSearchTool fetches it
  (Responses API only — requires ToolSearchTool on the agent).
  **strict_json_schema=True** enforces OpenAI strict mode.
  **timeout_behavior**: 'error_as_result' returns msg to model;
  'raise_exception' raises ToolTimeoutError.
  **tool_namespace()** groups tools under shared namespace metadata
  for Responses API tool search.
end note

note bottom of FuncSchema
  Built by **function_schema()** factory via introspection.
  Auto-detects docstring style (google/numpy/sphinx) via griffe.
  Supports **Annotated[T, 'description']** and **Pydantic Field**
  for argument metadata.
  **takes_context=True** strips RunContextWrapper/ToolContext from
  the Pydantic model but still injects it at call time.
end note

note bottom of ToolGuardrailFunctionOutput
  **Tool Guardrails** fire per function-tool invocation.
  Use behavior variants: allow / reject_content / raise_exception.
  ---
  **Agent Guardrails** (InputGuardrail/OutputGuardrail) fire at
  agent I/O boundaries and use boolean tripwire_triggered.
  InputGuardrail.run_in_parallel=True (default) runs concurrently
  with agent; False blocks start (prevents token waste, adds latency).
end note

note right of ToolOriginType
  Tracks provenance:
  FUNCTION — plain @function_tool
  MCP — from MCP server
  AGENT_AS_TOOL — agent-as-tool pattern
end note

@enduml
